# Personal learning material — kept on disk, not in the repo.
# The canonical copy lives in kotlin-LEARNING/LEARNING_STRATEGY.md
# and is synced to other repos via the LEARNING_STRATEGY.md drift policy.
LEARNING_STRATEGY.md

# Personal planning notes — kept on disk, not in the repo.
# Includes docs/intellij-plugin-plan.md and any future WIP files.
# Note: this only matches the top-level docs/ directory. Sibling modules
# under catoscript-libs/*/ have their own docs/devplan.md that ARE tracked
# (see AGENTS.md §3b for the sibling-module convention).
/docs/

# VS Code extension packages — build artifacts, regenerated via
# 'npx @vscode/vsce package' from the editor/ folder.
*.vsix

